  <scopecontent id="aspace_e71852ab853614b761796fb84e122ef8">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Campaign posters and other paraphernalia from the major political parties in the Hungarian elections of 1989-1990. Produced by some of Hungary's best graphic artists, these posters are a dramatic depiction of the clash of political symbols in the era of transition to democracy in Eastern Europe.</p>  </scopecontent>
